org.apache.derbyTesting.functionTests.util

Enum ProtocolTestGrammar

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ProtocolTestGrammar>
      • org.apache.derbyTesting.functionTests.util.ProtocolTestGrammar
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ProtocolTestGrammar>

    public enum ProtocolTestGrammar
extends java.lang.Enum<ProtocolTestGrammar>
    Describes the grammer / language for testing the DRDA protocol implementation used by Derby.

    Each command has a corresponding string, that can be used to specify a command sequence with text (for instance in a file).
